title: Jesus  & Mary Chain - Leeds University 27th November 1985
description:
THE JESUS AND MARY CHAIN
LEEDS University England 27-11-85
_________________________

un-beknown to everyone involved, they had just completely cracked open the british music scene with the release of the debut lp Psychocandy which would spur a rampant tangent of guitar based mayhem influencing the next 20 years of british music ranging from my bloody valentine, spacemen 3, stone roses, oasis etc etc.

so what do they do? a massive two date british tour of sub-30 min shows, showcasing their complete ineptitude. this is the first, and my first marychain gig.

source: xx/adobeaudition/cdwave/flac8/your recycle bin

where xx = nth generation audience recording, traded on tape back in 86.

In A Hole
Just Like Honey
The Hardest Walk
Inside Me
Taste Of Cindy
--- good god, they&#039;re shit eh
The Living End
Jesus Fuck
You Trip Me Up

they were complete rubbish.
